<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="announce-vt">announce <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'naʊns/    美 /ə'naʊns/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>宣告；宣布：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Please remain seated; the winner of the prize will be announced soon.
请坐好，马上公布获奖者。</p><footer>2008 辽宁</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Mr White announced that he would go to China in February.
怀特先生宣布他将于二月份去中国。</p><footer>2008 全国</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(尤指在机场或火车站) 广播通知：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The pilot announced with apology that there would be a slight delay before setting down.
飞行员抱歉地通知，飞机会晚一点着陆。</p><footer>2010 四川</footer></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>宣布…的到来 / 出席：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Would you announce the guests as they come in?
客人来时你通报一声好吗？</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>announcer /ə'naʊnsə(r)/ n [C]  </p></div>